tourBios.exmtStatus: Finished 7th at 2015 Web.com Tour Qualifying Tournament
tourBios.carHigh: 2015: Finished T13 at the Florida Qualifying Tournament, with rounds of 67-70-68-68...Added a T12 at the Syncrude Boreal Open, the third event of the Tour season...Continued his strong play with a T8 at The Players Cup...Shared the 54-hole lead at the Staal Foundation Open but stumbled to a final round 74 to finish T9...Eagled the 72nd hole at The Great Waterway Classic to T2...Shared the 54-hole lead again at The Wildfire Invitational but a final-round 73 halted his momentum and T10...Ended the season 18th on the Order of Merit to earn an exemption in the second stage of the Web.com Tour Qualifying Tournament.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Named Big South Freshman of the Year at Liberty University in 2010-11...Spring stroke average his freshman year ranks as the third best in program history...Named Big South All-Conference selection as a sophomore and junior...Finished four years at Liberty with 15 top-10 finishes.
tourBios.personal: Won't switch balls if he hasn't made a bogey...Favorite sports teams are the Cleveland Cavaliers and the Atlanta Braves...Dream foursome would include Jack Nicklaus, Tiger Woods and LeBron James...Bucket list includes attending competitions at a World Cup and an Olympics.
